unk-share-footage-of-the-first-time-pharrell-williams-heard-get-lucky-3514913">Pharrell 第一次听到“Get Lucky”和“Lose Yourself to Dance”的</a>视频，以纪念“Random Access Memories”十周年。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-pharrells-new-swae-lee-and-rauw-alejandro-collaboration-airplane-tickets-3556422">聆听 Pharrell 的 Swae Lee 和 Rauw Alejandro 合作新作《Airplane Tickets》一</a>文首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
